---
title: "Home Page"
layout: base.njk

---

  <main id="main">
      <section class="hero" aria-label="Bear Limo hero">
        <div class="hero-media" aria-hidden="true">
      <picture>
        {# Checks if a webp version exists, otherwise falls back dynamically #}
        {% if hero.image_webp %}
          <source srcset="{{ hero.image_webp }}" type="image/webp">
        {% endif %}
        <img src="{{ hero.image_jpg | default('assets/img/hero.jpg') }}" 
             alt="Black stretch limousine on a wet nighttime city street" 
             width="1920" 
             height="1080" 
             fetchpriority="high" 
             decoding="async">
      </picture>

        </div>
        <div class="container hero-inner">
          <span class="hero-eyebrow">{{hero.eyebrow}}</span>
          <h1>{{ hero.heading}}</h1>
          <p class="hero-sub">{{ hero.subtext}}</p>
          <div class="hero-cta">
          {% if hero.primary_cta.link %}
            <a class="btn btn-solid" href="{{ hero.primary_cta.link }}" rel="noopener" target="_blank">{{ hero.primary_cta.text | default('Get an Instant Quote') }}</a>
            {% endif %}
            {% if hero.secondary_cta.link %}
            <a class="btn" href=" {{ hero.secondary_cta.link }}">{{ hero.secondary_cta.text | default('Explore the Fleet') }}</a>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-scroll" aria-hidden="true">Scroll</div>
      </section>


      <style>
        /* Container Layout */
.hero-intro-section {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 3rem auto;
  padding: 0 1.5rem;
  text-align: left; /* Change to center if you want a centered hero alignment */
}

.header-container {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.5rem; /* Controls the tight spacing between headings */
}

/* Small Top Heading Styling */
.top-subheading {
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin: 0;
  color: #666; /* Subtle grey for semantic separation, or remove to inherit */
}

/* Big Main Heading Styling */
.main-heading {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  line-height: 1.2;
  margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  color: inherit; /* No color added */
}

/* Description Styling */
.section-description {
  font-size: 1.125rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin: 0;
}

/* Link Styling */


a.accent-link {
  color: #d32f2f; /* Red accent option if needed */
}

/* Responsive Scaling */
@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .main-heading {
    font-size: 1.9rem;
  }
}
      </style>
      <section class="hero-intro-section" aria-labelledby="main-section-heading">
  <div class="header-container">
    <!-- Small Top Heading (Eyebrow text for context) -->
    <h3 class="top-subheading">Trending Insights</h3>
    
    <!-- Big Main Heading (Primary keyword target for this section) -->
    <h2 id="main-section-heading" class="main-heading">Chauffeur-Driven Luxury</h2>
    
    <!-- Description Paragraph -->
    <p class="section-description">
     Experience seamless ground transportation with our fleet of meticulously maintained luxury sedans, 
      SUVs, and stretch limousines. From prompt airport transfers to elegant wedding day transport, 
      our professional chauffeurs ensure safety, privacy, and unparalleled punctuality. Book your ride 
      today or explore our <a href="/fleet" class="accent-link">luxury fleet options</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

    <!-- SEO Core Copy Pillar Block -->
<section class="section" style="padding: clamp(40px, 6vw, 80px) 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line, #eaeaea);">
  <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
    
    <div style="margin-bottom: 40px; text-align: left;">
      <span class="eyebrow" style="text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--muted, #666);">Premium Ground Transportation</span>
      <h2 style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem); line-height: 1.15; font-weight: 700; margin: 8px 0 20px;">
        Professional Livery Network &amp; Executive Airport Car Service
      </h2>
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1.5em;">
        Navigating regional airport transfers or coordinate corporate group travel requires a dependable luxury network. Bear Limo operates an elite fleet of private black cars, late-model executive SUVs, and classic stretch limousines engineered to align perfectly with the dispatch standards of <a href="https://www.grandlimousine.com/" rel="noopener" target="_blank" style="color:red; text-decoration: underline !important; font-weight: 600;">Grand Limousine</a>. By bridging localized dispatch with unified nationwide standards, we provide seamless point-to-point travel across 27 primary U.S. metropolitan markets.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 32px;">
      
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px;">
          Reliable Chauffeured Black Cars for Corporate Roadshows
        </h3>
        <p style="line-height: 1.6; ; margin: 0;">
          Time is the ultimate luxury for executive travelers. Our professional chauffeur services eliminate transit friction through integrated flight tracking pipelines, dynamic traffic monitoring, and 24/7 dedicated customer service loops. From private aviation pickups at regional FBOs to multi-stop corporate itineraries, each reservation receives individual route scouting to ensure flawless, on-time arrivals.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px;;">
          Luxury Limousine Rentals &amp; Private Fleet Options
        </h3>
        <p style="line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
          Different occasions demand distinct vehicle parameters. Our comprehensive network handles diverse group sizes and aesthetic preferences, featuring pristine executive sedans for solo corporate drop-offs, spacious SUVs for small team loops, and premium party buses or stretch limousines for weddings and gala events. Every vehicle is deep-cleaned daily and managed by licensed, intensely vetted professional drivers.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px;">
          Transparent Multi-City Billing Structures
        </h3>
        <p style="line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
          We believe in absolute billing transparency. All quotes generated through our direct connection with the Grand Limousine scheduling matrix feature all-inclusive initial layouts—incorporating base rates, local regulatory fees, tolls, and baseline chauffeur gratuities. This eliminates unexpected pricing spikes, allowing travel managers and individual passengers to budget their transportation allocations with absolute certainty.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- SEO Tip: Use a semantic container with a descriptive ID or class -->
 <style>
  /* Layout Styling */
.split-layout {
  display: flex;
  gap: 2rem;
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 1rem;
}

.column-left {
  flex: 2; /* Takes up 2/3 of the width */
}

.column-right {
  flex: 1; /* Takes up 1/3 of the width */
}

/* Typography & Color Rules */
h2, h3 {
  color: inherit; /* No color added; inherits default text color */
  font-size: 1.75rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

a {
  color: inherit; /* Standard links do not add color */

}

/* Explicit exception rule for red links */
a.accent-link {
  color: #d32f2f; /* Solid, accessible red color */
}

/* Responsive adjustment for smaller screens */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .split-layout {
    flex-direction: column;
  }
}
 </style>
